text: Kim Yoo-jin or Kim Yu-jin () is a Korean name. "Kim" () is the family name. "Yoo-jin" () is the given name. In English, "Yoo-jin" is written "Yu-jin" sometimes. It may refer to: * Kim Yoo-jin (footballer, born 1983), South Korean male footballer * Kim Yu-jin (taekwondo, born 1991), South Korean female taekwondo practitioner * Kim Yu-jin (taekwondo, born 2000), South Korean female taekwondo practitioner
title: Kim Yoo-jin
